Before running the notebook:

Ensure Python 3.x is installed.

Install the required packages (can use pip install -r requirements.txt).

The notebook retrieves live data from the Fruityvice API — ensure an internet connection.

Run cells sequentially to reproduce all analyses, visualizations, and segmentation insights.

Tip: The notebook is structured to first perform data retrieval and cleaning, then exploratory data analysis, followed by purpose-based segmentation and visualization of nutritional patterns.
